data.description:
Incredible Opportunity! Mostly original 3 bedroom/2 bathroom mountain cottage on a large parcel PLUS 3 ADDITIONAL parcels comprising 2 ADDITIONAL home sites (and ADU's) on over 2 beautiful acres.
The 4 Assessor Parcel Numbers are: 075-181-100 (24,000 sf), 075-183-010 (18,000 sf), 075-173-110 (30,000 sf) & 075-173-120 (20,000 sf). Senate Bill 9 should assist/improve development options and opportunities. Value is in both the existing home and potential for a total of 3 houses and 3 ADU's. Many options: build out together, live in one as you build others, or keep for future use. Great for extended family or friends. Exclusive Portola Valley and Woodside Schools. The properties have bay views, Cal Water, and a nice mix of trees. Some of the parcels are accessible via Sequoia Way. First time on market in 50 years.
